*Define prompt engineering and discuss its importance in interacting with AI models.

-Prompt engineering is about crafting questions or statements to get the best possible responses from Al models.

*Provide an example of a vague prompt and then improve it by making it clear, specific, and concise. Explain why the improved prompt is more effective.
-“Help me improve my productivity at work,”
-improved prompt:“Present three proven strategies to reduce distractions and improve productivity during work from home” the improved prompt is more effective because it's detailed and concise 
